Employee Anniversary 20 Yrs Decorative Formal Plum Card

Top 5! Employee Anniversary 20 Yrs Decorative Formal Plum Card – Anniversary Cards This item is trending! Employee Anniversary 20 Yrs Decorative Formal Plum Card help you save during this period Employee Anniversary 20 Yrs Decorative Formal Plum Card You can read more about itThis is a formal, yet decoratively stylish Employee 20th Year Anniversary Card.

The design has been created within a plum color scheme and features the number 20, center top, with each of the numbers, 2 and 0 in a decorative text box. The numbers are written in an elegantly curved font with a digitally created gold foil effect overlay and set against a black background. Underneath the numbers is the word ‘YEARS’, in a matching font and overlay to the numbers and set against a dark jade background.

In the lower section of the design, on a gently curved, multi-bordered text box, is the text ‘Happy Anniversary’, written in a beautifully flowing, script style font, with decorative swashes. This text too has a digitally created, gold foil effect overlay and is set against a black background.

PLEASE NOTE : The gold foil effect in this design was created digitally.

Natalie Kinnear Cards
